name: Watto's Box
Lore: 'Fortunes are won and lost every day on the Outer Rim. Watto is a master at getting his cut.',
Text: 'Deploy on table if all of your race totals = 0. When a player wins a Podrace, adds 5 to the amount retrieved. When a player loses a Podrace, adds 5 to the amount lost. (Immune to Alter.)',
